contentrichtext.text: {{wiktionary|interplay}} '''Interplay''' may refer to: * [[Interplay (John Coltrane album)|''Interplay'' (John Coltrane album)]], a 1957 album by jazz musician John Coltrane * [[Interplay (ballet)]], Jerome Robbins, 1945 * [[Interplay (Bill Evans album)]], a 1962 album by jazz musician Bill Evans * [[Interplay Entertainment]], video game publisher * [[World Interplay]], an Australian young playwrights festival * [[Interplay Europe]], a festival for young playwrights in Europe {{disambig}}
